citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:04PM on 16-
FEB-23.
This inspector attempted unsuccessfully to contact the licensee via the telephone on file, by text message, and by
electronic mail. Also, at 12:20PM, this inspector knocked on the facility's front door, and rang the doorbell; no response.
Optimal hours for future inspections are to be discussed and re-established.
Additional Inspectors:
KRISTIN NAPOLI, SUPERVISORY ANIMAL CARE SPECIALISTEnd Section
